ChoiceOptionDto - Class in com.intland.codebeamer.persistence.dto
Since CB-7.3 (tracker) field status/choice options are stored as/wrapped into special types of artifacts.
Note! We cannot simply make TrackerChoiceOptionDto extend ArtifactDto because IdentifiableDto.getId() is the stereotype option id (only unique within the same field), whereas IdentifiableDto.getId() is the unique object id of the object/option definition and the stereotype option id is stored in ArtifactDto.getGenericReferenceId() .
